      "content": "hey, i just tripped while running and my ankle is super swollen. i cant really walk on it right now without it hurting a ton, but it doesnt feel like the bone is broken or anything. i rly dont want to go to the ER if i dont have to lol. do u think i can just do the RICE thing (rest, ice, compression, elevation) for a few days and see if it gets better?",
